headline: Trump: No requests to pardon Sean 'Diddy' Combs, but will look at the facts
summary: WASHINGTON/NEW YORK -President Donald Trump said on Friday that no one has asked him to pardon Sean Diddy Combs but that he would look at the facts of the hip-hop mogul's case. ...
